Flow.description: StarTrack process that runs once a VOC incident record has been created or edited.

value.stringValue: AND( [Case].Case_RecordType_Name__c = 'Voice of Customer Enquiry', OR( AND( ISPICKVAL([Case].Origin, 'Web'), ISNEW()), AND( ISPICKVAL([Case].Origin, 'Email'), [Case].Send_Auto_Response_Email__c, NOT([Case].Auto_Email_Response_sent__c))), [Case].SuppliedEmail <> null, NOT(BEGINS([Case].SuppliedEmail, 'noreply')), NOT(BEGINS([Case].SuppliedEmail, 'no-reply')), NOT(BEGINS([Case].SuppliedEmail, 'postmaster')), NOT(BEGINS([Case].SuppliedEmail, 'mailer-daemon')), NOT(CONTAINS( LOWER($Setup.StarTrack_Settings__c.Blacklisted_Sender_Email_Addresses__c), LOWER([Case].SuppliedEmail))), NOT(CONTAINS( LOWER($Setup.StarTrack_Settings__c.Domains_Excluded_From_Auto_Response__c), LOWER(RIGHT([Case].SuppliedEmail, LEN([Case].SuppliedEmail) - FIND("@", [Case].SuppliedEmail))))))

formulas.expression: AND( {!myVariable_current.Case_RecordType_Name__c} = 'Voice of Customer Enquiry', OR( AND( ISPICKVAL({!myVariable_current.Origin}, 'Web'), ISNEW()), AND( ISPICKVAL({!myVariable_current.Origin}, 'Email'), {!myVariable_current.Send_Auto_Response_Email__c}, NOT({!myVariable_current.Auto_Email_Response_sent__c}))), {!myVariable_current.SuppliedEmail} <> null, NOT(BEGINS({!myVariable_current.SuppliedEmail}, 'noreply')), NOT(BEGINS({!myVariable_current.SuppliedEmail}, 'no-reply')), NOT(BEGINS({!myVariable_current.SuppliedEmail}, 'postmaster')), NOT(BEGINS({!myVariable_current.SuppliedEmail}, 'mailer-daemon')), NOT(CONTAINS( LOWER({!$Setup.StarTrack_Settings__c.Blacklisted_Sender_Email_Addresses__c}), LOWER({!myVariable_current.SuppliedEmail}))), NOT(CONTAINS( LOWER({!$Setup.StarTrack_Settings__c.Domains_Excluded_From_Auto_Response__c}), LOWER(RIGHT({!myVariable_current.SuppliedEmail}, LEN({!myVariable_current.SuppliedEmail}) - FIND("@", {!myVariable_current.SuppliedEmail}))))))
